thread.title_full: One killed in plane crash near New Tecumseth | CP24.com

author: Codi Wilson, CP24.com
title: One killed in plane crash near New Tecumseth
text:
Ontario Provincial Police say one person has died after a small plane crashed near New Tecumseth Saturday afternoon.
According to police, the plane hit hydro lines shortly before the crash, which occurred near Tottenham Road and the 7th Line.
The age and gender of the victim is not known at this time.
Two investigators with the Transportation Safety Board have been called in to probe the circumstances around the crash.
